      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<ab>Success! (This) upright slab placed on the south side of the eastern 
	gate of the Mahācaitya of the Blessed one, (is) the pious gift of ...
	the daughter of the householder 
	<persName key="pers:Am-Candramukha">Candramukha</persName>, an inhabitant
	of <placeName key="pl:Turughura">Turughura</placeName>, and of ... 
	and of the hālikā <persName key="pers:Am-Bādhā">Bādhā</persName>
	amd her granddaughter <persName key="pers:Am-Bhadrā">Bhadrā</persName>.</ab>
      </div>
